snippet.title: Fallout: Nuevo México (Teaser)
snippet.description:

America, 2166. Enter the post-apocalyptic nuclear-radiated wastes of New Mexico and explore its darkest secrets, meet the insanity, edgy, and comedic relief a Classic Fallout would give you while role-playing as whatever you wish. 

Plot details to be revealed. 

Prepare for the Future!
